1
00:00:03,480 --> 00:00:07,430
Intermission

2
00:00:10,930 --> 00:00:14,810
Fields that need no tilling...

3
00:00:15,060 --> 00:00:17,600
But why?

4
00:00:18,310 --> 00:00:21,100
If fields don't need to be tilled...

5
00:00:21,100 --> 00:00:24,480
...why do people do it anyway?

6
00:00:25,600 --> 00:00:26,900
Why do you think?

7
00:00:28,530 --> 00:00:30,120
Well...

8
00:00:30,370 --> 00:00:34,970
...isn't it because there's a
better yield if you till the soil?

9
00:00:35,220 --> 00:00:39,560
It's true that if you till the soil, you
can increase the yield slightly.

10
00:00:39,770 --> 00:00:42,020
By using up the reserve of nutrients...

11
00:00:42,020 --> 00:00:45,160
...that were accumulated in the soil.

12
00:00:45,370 --> 00:00:48,250
But that won't last forever.

13
00:00:48,460 --> 00:00:50,580
Huh? Why?

14
00:00:50,880 --> 00:00:54,250
The soil will die if you till it too much.

15
00:00:54,250 --> 00:00:56,000
The soil will die?

16
00:00:56,670 --> 00:01:00,380
That's because the world of the bugs, worms...

17
00:01:00,380 --> 00:01:04,180
...and the tiniest creatures in the
soil that you can't even see...

18
00:01:04,180 --> 00:01:05,970
...is destroyed.

19
00:01:05,970 --> 00:01:06,620
Huh?

20
00:01:07,220 --> 00:01:10,050
To them, tilling is worse than...

21
00:01:10,050 --> 00:01:14,920
...the kind of destruction you
get from carpet-bombing in war.

22
00:01:15,920 --> 00:01:17,220
But...

23
00:01:17,520 --> 00:01:21,630
...even the fields that are tilled
can yield some good crops.

24
00:01:22,230 --> 00:01:24,700
That's because they use fertilizers.

25
00:01:24,900 --> 00:01:28,670
To replace the nutrients that were
provided by the dead creatures.

26
00:01:28,670 --> 00:01:31,270
But by giving the soil fertilizer...

27
00:01:31,270 --> 00:01:34,640
...can't you get nice, big vegetables and good rice?

28
00:01:34,970 --> 00:01:38,310
Of course, the plants will grow
well if you give the soil fertilizer.

29
00:01:38,310 --> 00:01:42,480
But what if you gave it more than you had to...

30
00:01:42,480 --> 00:01:45,450
...and you just get vegetables that are too big?

31
00:01:45,620 --> 00:01:46,880
Too big?

32
00:01:48,020 --> 00:01:49,770
That's never a problem.

33
00:01:49,770 --> 00:01:52,350
People always want bigger vegetables.

34
00:01:52,350 --> 00:01:54,560
But if people get too big...

35
00:01:54,560 --> 00:01:56,690
...they get heavy and become slow.

36
00:01:56,690 --> 00:02:00,450
Well, that might be the case with humans...

37
00:02:00,860 --> 00:02:03,700
Too much is as bad as too little, they say.

38
00:02:03,700 --> 00:02:07,990
People and vegetables, cows
and pigs are all the same.

39
00:02:08,240 --> 00:02:12,230
With a lack of nutrition, they get thin and weak...

40
00:02:12,230 --> 00:02:14,680
...if there's too much, they get too fat...

41
00:02:15,300 --> 00:02:16,670
...and get weak?

42
00:02:19,120 --> 00:02:21,080
They get weak...

43
00:02:21,080 --> 00:02:23,250
...and the bugs come...

44
00:02:24,220 --> 00:02:27,020
When the wind blows, the cooper benefits.

45
00:02:27,820 --> 00:02:30,560
If you till the land, the soil becomes weak.

46
00:02:30,860 --> 00:02:34,260
Because the soil becomes weak,
fertilizers become necessary.

47
00:02:34,260 --> 00:02:37,630
The fields you give fertilizers
to get eaten up by insects.

48
00:02:37,630 --> 00:02:42,510
The more you overfeed livestock,
the more they will tend to become ill.

49
00:02:42,510 --> 00:02:46,210
And in order to get rid of those insects and viruses...

50
00:02:46,210 --> 00:02:47,810
...we spray the fields with insecticide...

51
00:02:47,810 --> 00:02:49,920
...or give the livestock medicine.

52
00:02:50,220 --> 00:02:53,580
Vegetables and animals given too
much insecticide and medicine...

53
00:02:53,580 --> 00:02:55,700
...get weaker and weaker...

54
00:02:56,650 --> 00:02:58,890
They may look bigger...

55
00:02:58,890 --> 00:03:03,000
...but if people were to eat
crops that have gotten weaker...

56
00:03:04,030 --> 00:03:05,500
No...

57
00:03:09,850 --> 00:03:15,250
A teraz sa stane zázrak na tejto planéte.

58
00:03:30,300 --> 00:03:32,330
Spala si dobre?

59
00:03:33,470 --> 00:03:35,410
Kde sme teraz?

60
00:03:35,410 --> 00:03:38,850
Práve sme prešli Ashijyu,
o chvíľu budeme v Sannomyii.

61
00:03:38,850 --> 00:03:39,970
Hej?

62
00:03:43,250 --> 00:03:46,620
Je mi ľúto, že si tam
musel nechať svoju motorku.

63
00:03:46,620 --> 00:03:47,890
To je v poriadku.

64
00:03:47,890 --> 00:03:49,820
Donútim otca, aby mi kúpil novú..

65
00:03:49,820 --> 00:03:52,090
Hej, to nie je správne.

66
00:03:52,090 --> 00:03:55,230
Popol popolu, prach prachu.

67
00:03:55,230 --> 00:03:58,160
Niekto možno nájde moju motorku
a zanesie ju do zberu.

68
00:03:58,160 --> 00:04:02,430
Tomu sa hovorí „recyklovanie“.

69
00:04:07,170 --> 00:04:08,140
Hej, hej.

70
00:04:09,880 --> 00:04:13,180
Ten starý pán v horách ťa dostal?

71
00:04:13,180 --> 00:04:14,170
Čo?

72
00:04:15,580 --> 00:04:16,980
Keď nad tým premýšľam...

73
00:04:16,980 --> 00:04:20,210
...boli sme s ním štyri dni
a ani nevieme ako sa volá.

74
00:04:21,790 --> 00:04:26,660
„ Meno by nemalo mať nič spoločné so stavom vecí.“

75
00:04:28,860 --> 00:04:31,160
Myslím, že ten dedko dostal aj teba.

76
00:04:34,830 --> 00:04:39,290
Arjuna pozemšťanka

77
00:04:41,840 --> 00:04:45,640
Diel piaty: Tiché hlasy

78
00:04:54,750 --> 00:04:57,690
Čo je to za pach?

79
00:04:57,690 --> 00:04:59,180
Ako je v meste?

80
00:04:59,890 --> 00:05:03,020
Dokážeš stále žiť tak, ako si žila doteraz?

81
00:05:05,730 --> 00:05:08,800
Prečo ma Chris stále špehuje?

82
00:05:08,800 --> 00:05:10,030
Ideme.

83
00:05:10,500 --> 00:05:12,840
Kam chceš ísť, Tokio?

84
00:05:12,840 --> 00:05:14,670
Ešte nemôžem ísť domov.

85
00:05:14,670 --> 00:05:17,610
Nebol som doma kvôli tebe už asi týždeň..

86
00:05:23,450 --> 00:05:24,610
Juna?

87
00:05:25,850 --> 00:05:29,220
Vedela som, že si to ty, Juna!
Aj ty, Tokio!

88
00:05:30,120 --> 00:05:31,920
Sayuri?

89
00:05:39,530 --> 00:05:42,830
Veliteľ Onizuka.

90
00:05:43,940 --> 00:05:45,530
To ste vy.

91
00:06:18,600 --> 00:06:21,910
To musí byť voda z Okusagy.

92
00:06:21,910 --> 00:06:27,180
Neobsahuje chlór ani dusičnan sodný.

93
00:06:29,680 --> 00:06:33,290
Zdá sa, že informácie týkajúce sa
vypuknutia záhadnej infekčnej choroby...

94
00:06:33,290 --> 00:06:35,250
...spôsobujúcej úplnú paralýzu...

95
00:06:35,250 --> 00:06:40,250
...úmyselne prenikli z austrálskej pobočky S. E. E. D-u.

96
00:06:41,090 --> 00:06:45,220
Myslíte si, že to má spojitosť
s geneticky upravovaným jedlom?

97
00:06:45,730 --> 00:06:48,970
Zdá sa, že ide o nový typ
smrteľnej nákazlivej črevnej baktérie...

98
00:06:48,970 --> 00:06:50,800
...podobnej botulotoxínu.

99
00:06:50,800 --> 00:06:52,330
Viac nie je známe.

100
00:06:53,040 --> 00:06:55,910
Nákaza vypukla v Kobe, Osake, Gifu...

101
00:06:55,910 --> 00:06:59,710
...a ďalších mestách na západe Japonska.

102
00:07:01,880 --> 00:07:04,180
A čo to TI-2 dievča...

103
00:07:04,180 --> 00:07:06,050
...Juna?

104
00:07:06,790 --> 00:07:08,250
Môžeme ju použiť?

105
00:07:08,250 --> 00:07:10,920
Ešte nebola úplne prebudená.

106
00:07:11,990 --> 00:07:13,390
Chápem.

107
00:07:20,130 --> 00:07:24,260
Znamená to, že sa môžeme spoľahnúť
iba na Chrisa, TI-1.

108
00:07:33,950 --> 00:07:38,440
Ak nebudeš jesť, dostaneš infúziu..

109
00:07:39,890 --> 00:07:41,650
Prosím, Chris.

110
00:07:43,260 --> 00:07:44,480
Prečo sa usmievaš?

111
00:07:45,190 --> 00:07:46,330
Iba ma napadlo...

112
00:07:46,330 --> 00:07:50,390
...že aj niekto iný má problémy s jedením.

113
00:07:52,060 --> 00:07:54,090
Itadakimasu!

114
00:07:56,940 --> 00:07:59,400
O tejto chuti som sníval.

115
00:08:01,210 --> 00:08:02,480
Nebudeš jesť?

116
00:08:04,340 --> 00:08:07,310
Premýšľala som nad niečím,
čo povedal starý pán.

117
00:08:08,080 --> 00:08:10,740
O tom, že všetko čo zjem,
sa stane mojou časťou.

118
00:08:11,980 --> 00:08:13,320
Nie, nie.

119
00:08:13,690 --> 00:08:15,220
Ak začneš takto premýšľať...

120
00:08:15,220 --> 00:08:17,280
...nebudeš môcť zjesť nič v meste.

121
00:08:19,330 --> 00:08:23,030
Prepáčte. Niečo ma zdržalo.

122
00:08:23,030 --> 00:08:25,290
Ospravedlňujem sa, že ste na mňa čakali.

123
00:08:26,030 --> 00:08:27,360
Už som tu.

124
00:08:28,030 --> 00:08:30,370
Juna, to je skvelá ozdoba!

125
00:08:30,370 --> 00:08:32,060
Kde si to kúpila? V Moto-Koh?

126
00:08:32,710 --> 00:08:35,140
Toto?

127
00:08:35,140 --> 00:08:36,570
No...

128
00:08:36,880 --> 00:08:39,250
Hej, kde si nechala okuliare?

129
00:08:39,250 --> 00:08:40,810
Všimol si si to?

130
00:08:40,810 --> 00:08:44,180
Musím si dať predpísať nové,
tak dnes mám kontaktné šošovky.

131
00:08:45,220 --> 00:08:47,450
Bez okuliarov vyzeráš lepšie.

132
00:08:47,450 --> 00:08:48,290
Myslíš?!

133
00:08:48,290 --> 00:08:49,960
Mám radosť, aj keď to nie je pravda.

134
00:08:49,960 --> 00:08:52,420
Je to pravda! Vyzeráš skvele!

135
00:09:00,700 --> 00:09:02,570
Čo je to?

136
00:09:11,480 --> 00:09:12,170
Čo je to?!

137
00:09:13,450 --> 00:09:17,250
Zástupca riaditeľa, pán Tanabe sa ma na vás pýtal.

138
00:09:17,250 --> 00:09:20,320
Povedala som mu, že je to vaša vec....

139
00:09:20,320 --> 00:09:24,550
Neboj sa, nepovedala som mu nič divné...

140
00:09:27,590 --> 00:09:29,660
Takže je to len klebeta?

141
00:09:29,660 --> 00:09:31,900
Nie tak celkom.

142
00:09:31,900 --> 00:09:34,130
Kde ste vy dvaja vlastne boli?

143
00:09:34,130 --> 00:09:36,170
Urobili sme si malý výlet na vidiek.

144
00:09:36,170 --> 00:09:37,800
Pomáhali sme na poli.

145
00:09:39,370 --> 00:09:41,000
Jasné!

146
00:09:42,140 --> 00:09:45,380
Neviem si predstaviť, že ty, bohatý synáčik...

147
00:09:45,380 --> 00:09:47,570
...by si robil manuálnu prácu!

148
00:09:48,880 --> 00:09:51,180
-Je to pravda?
-Je to pravda!

149
00:09:51,180 --> 00:09:52,840
-Prisahám!
-Klameš!

150
00:09:53,250 --> 00:09:56,020
-Klameš.
-Tak klamem.

151
00:09:59,030 --> 00:10:00,790
Ako je v meste?

152
00:10:00,790 --> 00:10:04,090
Dokážeš stále žiť ako si žila doteraz?

153
00:10:06,030 --> 00:10:08,300
Mal som špinavé ruky od práce!

154
00:10:08,300 --> 00:10:11,240
Hej, hej, verím ti.

155
00:10:11,240 --> 00:10:12,370
Už viem!

156
00:10:12,370 --> 00:10:15,470
Priateľský zápas proti Trojke bol úžasný!

157
00:10:15,470 --> 00:10:17,580
Pamätáš si na to dievča,
čo sa objavilo na krajskom kole...

158
00:10:17,580 --> 00:10:20,250
...mala si vidieť jej lukostreľbu!

159
00:10:20,250 --> 00:10:23,450
Akoby jej duša splynula s terčom.

160
00:10:23,450 --> 00:10:24,580
Aj tréner povedal...

161
00:10:24,580 --> 00:10:28,780
...že taký talent sa objaví raz za 20 rokov..

162
00:10:29,220 --> 00:10:30,480
Juna?

163
00:10:31,620 --> 00:10:32,680
Juna?

164
00:10:33,190 --> 00:10:34,520
Čo sa stalo?

165
00:10:34,960 --> 00:10:37,560
Juna, hej Juna!

166
00:10:37,560 --> 00:10:39,570
Necítiš sa dobre?

167
00:10:39,570 --> 00:10:40,600
Čo sa stalo?

168
00:10:40,600 --> 00:10:42,090
Si v poriadku?

169
00:10:49,610 --> 00:10:51,410
Počkaj chvíľu!

170
00:10:52,810 --> 00:10:54,510
Prečo si urazená?

171
00:10:54,510 --> 00:10:55,880
Nie som urazená.

172
00:10:56,380 --> 00:10:57,750
Hej, ale...

173
00:11:00,550 --> 00:11:02,860
Čo som ti urobila?

174
00:11:02,860 --> 00:11:06,760
Vyzeráš, ako by ťa niečo trápilo...

175
00:11:07,090 --> 00:11:08,080
Myslíš...

176
00:11:09,060 --> 00:11:12,430
Ja ti vážne nerozumiem.

177
00:11:13,100 --> 00:11:15,700
Dokonca som si myslela,
že si s Tokiom ušla z domu...

178
00:11:15,700 --> 00:11:19,690
...ale vy dvaja ste len divný párik,
ktorý sa ešte ani nepobozkal.

179
00:11:22,780 --> 00:11:27,080
Chcem iba, aby ste spolu vychádzali.
Nechápeš to?

180
00:11:27,080 --> 00:11:28,600
To platí aj pre teba, Oshima-kun.

181
00:11:30,520 --> 00:11:33,450
Ten chodník sa hýbe...

182
00:11:35,090 --> 00:11:35,920
Oshima-kun?!

183
00:11:35,920 --> 00:11:36,820
Tokio!

184
00:11:38,360 --> 00:11:41,590
Mama! Mama! Otvor dvere!

185
00:11:42,330 --> 00:11:43,490
Juna?

186
00:11:43,700 --> 00:11:44,990
Si to ty, Juna?

187
00:11:47,770 --> 00:11:51,300
Juna, kde si bola?!
Zomierala som od strachu!!

188
00:11:51,300 --> 00:11:52,710
Prepáč, mami!

189
00:11:52,710 --> 00:11:54,940
Mohli by ste, prosím zavolať sanitku?

190
00:11:54,940 --> 00:11:57,000
Oshima-kun je vážne chorý!

191
00:11:58,240 --> 00:12:01,180
Áno. Presne tak.

192
00:12:01,180 --> 00:12:03,210
Meno je Ariyoshi.

193
00:12:03,620 --> 00:12:06,140
Áno, ponáhľajte sa prosím.

194
00:12:07,150 --> 00:12:09,790
Takže okrem zvracania má aj kŕče...

195
00:12:09,790 --> 00:12:12,760
...a nepravidelné dýchanie.

196
00:12:12,760 --> 00:12:16,130
Presne tak. Zdá sa, že má veľké bolesti.

197
00:12:16,130 --> 00:12:17,430
Rozumiem.

198
00:12:17,430 --> 00:12:19,900
Hneď tam pošleme sanitku.

199
00:12:20,200 --> 00:12:22,390
Robte to, čo vám povie zdravotná služba.

200
00:12:29,480 --> 00:12:30,940
Neboj sa, Tokio.

201
00:12:30,940 --> 00:12:32,850
Sanitka tu bude každú chvíľu.

202
00:12:32,850 --> 00:12:34,950
Vypi to, Oshima-kun!!

203
00:12:34,950 --> 00:12:37,870
No tak, otvor ústa.

204
00:12:41,590 --> 00:12:42,960
Len pokojne.

205
00:12:42,960 --> 00:12:44,250
Pokojne.

206
00:12:44,720 --> 00:12:45,490
Tak.

207
00:12:56,240 --> 00:12:57,740
Čo sa deje?!

208
00:12:57,740 --> 00:12:59,200
Práve si zobral liek!

209
00:13:01,310 --> 00:13:02,370
Tokio!

210
00:13:02,810 --> 00:13:03,640
Tokio.

211
00:13:13,350 --> 00:13:14,220
Juna!

212
00:13:17,290 --> 00:13:20,620
Arjuna pozemšťanka

213
00:13:21,360 --> 00:13:23,500
Kaine, kde si teraz?

214
00:13:23,500 --> 00:13:26,830
Kaine! Tvoja sestra je veľmi chorá!

215
00:13:27,200 --> 00:13:29,970
Čo? Ideš teraz von s priateľmi?

216
00:13:29,970 --> 00:13:31,870
O čom to hovoríš?

217
00:13:31,870 --> 00:13:35,210
-Juna je tvoja sestra!
-Je to také zlé, že musí byť v karanténe?

218
00:13:35,210 --> 00:13:36,010
Hovorím ti, že...

219
00:13:36,010 --> 00:13:38,240
-Musíme zabrániť rozšíreniu nákazy.
-Vráť sa okamžite domov!

220
00:13:38,240 --> 00:13:39,970
Musíme podniknúť bezpečnostné opatrenia.

221
00:13:44,580 --> 00:13:47,210
TI-2. Potvrdzujem biologickú reakciu.

222
00:13:47,720 --> 00:13:50,020
Biologický senzor sa kalibruje.

223
00:13:50,020 --> 00:13:51,060
TI-2 odpovedá.

224
00:13:51,060 --> 00:13:55,030
Postupuje z dvanástnika do tenkého čreva.

225
00:13:55,030 --> 00:13:59,000
Kým nezistíme, či ide
o toxickú látku alebo vírus...

226
00:13:59,000 --> 00:14:01,690
...nedávajte chlapcovi žiadne antibiotiká.

227
00:14:02,100 --> 00:14:03,970
Ak by sa vyskytla alergická reakcia na liek....

228
00:14:03,970 --> 00:14:06,030
...neboli by sme schopní ju zastaviť.

229
00:14:08,610 --> 00:14:10,910
Hups. Máme problém.

230
00:14:10,910 --> 00:14:15,450
Máme tu odpoveď mikro Raaja aj z tela TI-2.

231
00:14:15,450 --> 00:14:19,040
Chcete povedať, že Raaja
sa rozšíril aj do Juny, teda TI-2?!

232
00:14:19,320 --> 00:14:22,220
Ak sa to zhorší a ona zomrie...

233
00:14:22,220 --> 00:14:25,190
...máme šancu vystopovať,
kde skončí duševné telo TI-2...

234
00:14:25,190 --> 00:14:27,250
...po tom, čo fyzické telo zomrie.

235
00:14:28,990 --> 00:14:31,360
TI-2 sa dostala do hrubého čreva.

236
00:14:38,370 --> 00:14:39,670
Čože?

237
00:14:41,070 --> 00:14:45,340
Nehovorte mi, že som v Tokiovom tele!

238
00:14:47,380 --> 00:14:49,750
Užitočné bifidobaktérie a enterokoky...

239
00:14:49,750 --> 00:14:51,450
...a zlé klostrídiá perfringens a baktérie E.Coli...

240
00:14:51,450 --> 00:14:54,520
...rast celej bakteriálnej flóry klesol.

241
00:14:54,520 --> 00:14:58,360
Jeho imunita klesla o 10 percent.

242
00:14:58,360 --> 00:15:01,530
Pretože jeho črevné baktérie boli oslabené...

243
00:15:01,530 --> 00:15:04,550
...umožnilo to inváziu bakteriálneho Raaja.

244
00:15:05,660 --> 00:15:07,930
Steny hrubého čreva vylučujú lymfu.

245
00:15:26,950 --> 00:15:30,090
Zdá sa, že bakteriálny Raaja sa vylúčil spolu s lymfou...

246
00:15:30,090 --> 00:15:32,150
...a spôsobuje nepokoj v črevách.

247
00:15:47,310 --> 00:15:49,510
Raaja sa rozšíril do konečníka...

248
00:15:49,510 --> 00:15:51,380
Dýchanie pacienta je nepravidelné.

249
00:15:51,380 --> 00:15:52,710
Už viac nevydrží.

250
00:15:53,610 --> 00:15:54,610
Lekárskej sekcii.

251
00:15:54,610 --> 00:15:55,980
Dajte pacientovi antibiotiká.

252
00:15:55,980 --> 00:15:57,110
Je to zbytočné!

253
00:15:57,320 --> 00:16:00,590
Na základe analýzy pacientových
lymfatických žliaz...

254
00:16:00,590 --> 00:16:03,260
...sme objavili analgetiká, insekticídy...

255
00:16:03,260 --> 00:16:04,760
...konzervačné látky...

256
00:16:04,760 --> 00:16:07,490
...a takisto rastové hormóny.

257
00:16:07,490 --> 00:16:08,260
A...

258
00:16:08,260 --> 00:16:10,750
Protilátky používané v mäse...

259
00:16:11,600 --> 00:16:16,060
Zdá sa, že chemické a potravinové
prísady majú negatívny efekt.

260
00:16:17,440 --> 00:16:19,230
Útočia naňho zo všetkých strán!

261
00:16:26,350 --> 00:16:27,570
Dočerta!

262
00:16:29,920 --> 00:16:31,280
Hlupaňa.

263
00:16:32,050 --> 00:16:33,090
Nie, Chris!

264
00:16:33,090 --> 00:16:35,610
Zomrieš, ak pôjdeš v tomto stave!

265
00:16:42,330 --> 00:16:45,860
Ďalšie duchovné telo TI
sa hlási v blízkosti TI-2.

266
00:16:45,860 --> 00:16:46,890
To je Chris.

267
00:16:47,530 --> 00:16:49,160
Prečo bojuješ?

268
00:16:49,670 --> 00:16:50,770
Chris!

269
00:16:50,770 --> 00:16:53,710
Prečo?! Raaja je tu!

270
00:16:53,710 --> 00:16:55,770
Ak nebudem bojovať, Tokio zomrie!

271
00:16:56,580 --> 00:16:59,080
Čo si sa naučila v horách?

272
00:16:59,080 --> 00:16:59,910
Čo?

273
00:17:00,310 --> 00:17:02,780
Čo má toto spoločné s horami?!

274
00:17:04,050 --> 00:17:06,640
Musíš cítiť jeho skutočnú podobu.

275
00:17:07,150 --> 00:17:08,710
Sama.

276
00:17:12,690 --> 00:17:13,660
Ideme.

277
00:17:24,400 --> 00:17:29,030
Odrazy TI-1 a TI-2 sa presunuli do tela TI-2.

278
00:17:29,810 --> 00:17:30,870
Čo je to?!

279
00:17:31,410 --> 00:17:35,150
Nevieš nič o tom, čo sa deje v tvojom tele.

280
00:17:35,150 --> 00:17:38,320
Čo? Sme v mojom žalúdku?

281
00:17:38,320 --> 00:17:40,150
Odporné.

282
00:17:40,950 --> 00:17:44,480
Zdá sa ti špinavý? Hnusný?

283
00:17:44,760 --> 00:17:48,660
Nedokážeš prijať ani vlastné telo?

284
00:17:49,060 --> 00:17:51,000
Ani tvoje vlastné telo...

285
00:17:51,900 --> 00:17:53,470
Skús si spomenúť.

286
00:17:53,470 --> 00:17:56,700
Hora ti ukázala svoju skutočnú tvár.

287
00:17:56,800 --> 00:17:58,400
A čo tie polia?

288
00:17:58,400 --> 00:18:00,430
Hora? Polia?

289
00:18:00,640 --> 00:18:02,340
Skús si spomenúť.

290
00:18:02,340 --> 00:18:04,180
Na posvätnú horu...

291
00:18:04,180 --> 00:18:07,670
...a polia prekypujúce životom,
plné hmyzu a rastlín.

292
00:18:08,210 --> 00:18:12,170
...na skutočnú povahu aj tých
najmenších životných foriem.

293
00:18:18,690 --> 00:18:24,830
Hmyz a burina nie sú nepriatelia.

294
00:18:25,400 --> 00:18:28,630
Všetky majú svoju úlohu v kolobehu života.

295
00:18:29,900 --> 00:18:33,430
Je žalúdok to isté ako krajina?

296
00:18:36,110 --> 00:18:38,640
To TI-2 dievča je pozoruhodné.

297
00:18:38,640 --> 00:18:42,180
Má v tele veľké množstvo črevných baktérií.

298
00:18:42,180 --> 00:18:46,550
Počas jej pobytu v horách sa muselo
zvýšiť množstvo baktérií v jej tele...

299
00:18:46,550 --> 00:18:49,520
...to vysvetľuje, ako sa jej podarilo
potlačiť Raaju v sebe na minimum.

300
00:18:49,520 --> 00:18:50,610
-Blíži sa.

301
00:18:54,760 --> 00:18:55,890
Raaja?!

302
00:18:55,890 --> 00:18:57,200
Presne tak.

303
00:18:57,200 --> 00:18:59,130
Raaja sa rozšíril aj do tvojho tela.

304
00:18:59,330 --> 00:19:00,920
Aj do mňa?

305
00:19:01,970 --> 00:19:04,570
Raaja je v mojom tele...

306
00:19:04,570 --> 00:19:06,560
...a ja som si to vôbec nevšimla.

307
00:19:07,070 --> 00:19:10,710
A čo s tým chceš robiť?

308
00:19:11,180 --> 00:19:13,040
Čo teraz urobíš?

309
00:19:19,080 --> 00:19:20,890
V oblasti Tohoku pribudli ďalšie 2 obete nákazy.

310
00:19:20,890 --> 00:19:23,090
Zastavili sme dodávanie vody...

311
00:19:23,090 --> 00:19:23,950
Čo teraz...?

312
00:19:29,030 --> 00:19:30,360
Teta?

313
00:19:30,360 --> 00:19:32,330
Keď sa konečne vrátila domov...

314
00:19:32,330 --> 00:19:35,630
...myslím, že jej urobím jej obľúbené kushikatsu.

315
00:19:35,630 --> 00:19:37,100
Čo tým myslíte?

316
00:19:37,100 --> 00:19:39,170
Musíš byť tiež hladná.

317
00:19:39,170 --> 00:19:41,470
Spamätajte sa!

318
00:19:43,040 --> 00:19:45,240
Ak sa Juna nepreberie...

319
00:19:45,680 --> 00:19:49,270
...ako to vysvetlím jej milovanej zosnulej starkej?

320
00:19:50,720 --> 00:19:55,750
Moja starká mi raz povedala,
že ak je niekto veľmi chorý...

321
00:19:55,750 --> 00:19:57,460
...mal by vypiť liek z
jeho vlastnej pupočnej šnúry.

322
00:19:57,460 --> 00:19:58,420
Veliteľstvo!

323
00:19:58,420 --> 00:19:59,290
Áno, počula som to.

324
00:19:59,590 --> 00:20:00,590
No! Čo myslíte?

325
00:20:00,590 --> 00:20:02,360
Pracujem na tom.

326
00:20:03,760 --> 00:20:05,800
Toto by mohlo zabrať.

327
00:20:05,800 --> 00:20:07,670
Hormón z pupočnej šnúry.

328
00:20:07,670 --> 00:20:10,100
Enzým z doby, keď bolo telo len plod.

329
00:20:10,100 --> 00:20:13,370
Pupočná šnúra je ako skladisko baktérií.

330
00:20:13,370 --> 00:20:16,170
Možno sa nám podarí Raaja na chvíľu zadržať.

331
00:20:34,660 --> 00:20:36,690
Práve kopla..

332
00:20:38,030 --> 00:20:39,970
No tak, Kaine.

333
00:20:39,970 --> 00:20:41,200
Počuješ ma?

334
00:20:41,200 --> 00:20:45,700
Ale drahý. Ešte sa nenarodila.

335
00:20:45,700 --> 00:20:47,810
Konečne sme jej vymysleli meno.

336
00:20:47,810 --> 00:20:50,330
Možno by sme ho mali začať používať.

337
00:20:52,610 --> 00:20:56,570
Táto pupočná šnúra nepatrí June, ale Kaine.

338
00:21:00,050 --> 00:21:03,260
Kaine, poď už von.

339
00:21:03,260 --> 00:21:08,920
Keď sa narodíš, prestaneme
byť pár, ale budeme rodina.

340
00:21:13,370 --> 00:21:15,670
Teplo.

341
00:21:15,670 --> 00:21:17,530
Teplé svetlo.

342
00:21:18,240 --> 00:21:22,000
Svetlo, ktoré som cítila veľmi, veľmi dávno.

343
00:21:23,880 --> 00:21:25,310
Mama...

344
00:21:26,880 --> 00:21:29,750
Čo sa stalo? Čo je to?

345
00:21:32,450 --> 00:21:37,980
To je tlkot srdca,
ktoré dieťa počuje v maternici.

346
00:21:38,520 --> 00:21:41,750
Spomienka plodu, keď bol v mori maternice.

347
00:21:48,530 --> 00:21:50,500
Zaznamenávam rezonanciu so Zemou.

348
00:21:51,540 --> 00:21:55,140
Nie sú priatelia ani nepriatelia.

349
00:21:55,140 --> 00:21:58,630
Vy, malé stvorenia, spojte sa...

350
00:21:59,110 --> 00:22:03,910
...buďte jedno a vytvorte nový život.

351
00:22:13,830 --> 00:22:17,060
Užitočné baktérie v tele TI-2 rapídne rastú.

352
00:22:17,060 --> 00:22:19,530
Rast sa deje neuveriteľnou rýchlosťou!

353
00:22:19,530 --> 00:22:20,800
To nie je možné...

354
00:22:20,800 --> 00:22:23,900
Aj s pupočnou šnúrou to nemôže ísť tak rýchlo!

355
00:22:23,900 --> 00:22:25,400
Nie.

356
00:22:25,400 --> 00:22:27,840
To majú pravdepodobne na svedomí jej mozgové vlny.

357
00:22:27,840 --> 00:22:30,030
Nie, jej duša.

358
00:22:37,850 --> 00:22:40,180
Raaja mizne.

359
00:22:40,850 --> 00:22:45,020
Jej duša ovplyvnila život malých bytostí.

360
00:23:03,110 --> 00:23:03,980
Čo?

361
00:23:03,980 --> 00:23:05,910
TI-2 robí niečo veľmi zvláštne.

362
00:23:05,910 --> 00:23:06,840
Čo tým myslíte?

363
00:23:07,310 --> 00:23:08,470
Juna?

364
00:23:09,010 --> 00:23:10,280
Deje sa niečo?

365
00:23:10,950 --> 00:23:11,820
Tokio...

366
00:23:18,020 --> 00:23:21,290
Pacientove mozgové vlny sa zosynchronizovali s TI-2.

367
00:23:21,990 --> 00:23:23,160
Neuveriteľné.

368
00:23:23,160 --> 00:23:26,490
Črevné baktérie rastú aj v chlapcovi.

369
00:23:45,750 --> 00:23:47,050
Chris...

370
00:23:48,690 --> 00:23:51,250
Juna... Juna...

371
00:24:20,090 --> 00:24:21,090
Juna!

372
00:24:21,090 --> 00:24:23,880
Ty si ma vydesila...

373
00:24:23,990 --> 00:24:24,850
Mami...

374
00:24:27,260 --> 00:24:29,530
Už nikdy ma neopúšťaj.

375
00:24:29,530 --> 00:24:30,830
Prosím ťa.

376
00:24:32,300 --> 00:24:36,100
Prepáč, že som ti robila starosti.

377
00:24:36,770 --> 00:24:37,870
Tokio?

378
00:24:37,870 --> 00:24:39,000
Čo je s Tokiom?

379
00:24:39,000 --> 00:24:41,940
Povedali, že z najhoršieho je už vonku.

380
00:24:41,940 --> 00:24:43,580
Nemusíš sa báť.

381
00:24:43,580 --> 00:24:44,710
Naozaj?

382
00:24:44,710 --> 00:24:48,770
Doktor povedal, že keď
si odpočinie, bude v poriadku.

383
00:24:49,550 --> 00:24:51,180
Vďakabohu.

384
00:24:51,880 --> 00:24:55,840
Bolo milé od Sayuri,
že tu zostala celý čas.

385
00:24:56,220 --> 00:24:59,590
Je to ohľaduplné dievča.

386
00:25:01,360 --> 00:25:02,920
Sayuri...

387
00:25:04,830 --> 00:25:07,130
Juna? Si v poriadku?

388
00:25:08,430 --> 00:25:09,800
Mami, môj žalúdok...

389
00:25:09,800 --> 00:25:11,530
Zas ťa to bolí?

390
00:25:12,040 --> 00:25:13,730
Mám hlad.

391
00:25:14,440 --> 00:25:16,040
Vydrž chvíľu.

392
00:25:16,040 --> 00:25:18,440
Urobím ti ryžovú kašu.

393
00:25:18,740 --> 00:25:22,700
Arjuna pozemšťanka
